draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kawai Sōrō|ja|河合曾良|12=draft|12=draft}}, a haiku poet and one of the disciples of Shōmon Jūtetsu (born [[1649]]). * [[Kansei]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1799]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Asada Gōritsu|ja|麻田剛立|12=draft|12=draft}}, an astronomer (born [[1734]]).
