== Events == * {{ill|Tenkei|ja|天慶|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[938]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Shōhei|ja|承平 (日本)||12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Tenkei|ja|天慶|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}. * [[Shōkyō]] 2nd year / [[Genkō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – The Kamakura shogunate was overthrown when [[Nitta Yoshisada]] attacked Kamakura, forcing about 800 members of the [[Hōjō]] clan, including {{ill|Hōjō Takatoshi|ja|北条高時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, to commit suicide.
== Births == * Genbun 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1737]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieharu|ja|徳川家治|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 10th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[1786]]). * [[Bunka]] 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1815]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Asada Sōhaku|ja|浅田宗伯|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a physician of traditional Chinese medicine and Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (died [[1894]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1859]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tsubouchi Shōyō|ja|坪内逍遙|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a novelist (died [[1935]]).
== Deaths == * [[Yōshō (Southern Song)|Yōshō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[422]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – Emperor Wu of the Southern Song (【劉裕】), the first Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[356]]). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Motoki|ja|北条基時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 13th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1285]]). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Takatoshi|ja|北条高時|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 14th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate and 9th Detsū (born [[1303]]). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Sadakazu|ja|北条貞顕|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 15th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1278]]). * [[Ryakuō]] 1st year / [[Engen]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|ja|ユリウス暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1338]] {{ill|June 10|ja|6月10日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kitabatake Akiie|ja|北畠顕家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) (born [[1318]]). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)|lt=Tenshō Era|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1586]] {{ill|July 8|ja|7月8日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hachisuga Masakatsu|ja|蜂須賀正勝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a military commander (born [[1526]]). * [[Tenna]] 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1682]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Ikeda Mitsumasa|ja|池田光政|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, lord of the Okayama Domain in Bizen (born [[1609]]). * {{ill|Hōei|ja|宝永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1710]] {{ill|June 18|ja|6月18日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Kawai Sōrō|ja|河合曾良|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, a haiku poet and one of the disciples of Shōmon Jūtetsu (born [[1649]]). * [[Kansei]] 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} [[1799]] {{ill|June 25|ja|6月25日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Asada Gōritsu|ja|麻田剛立|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}}, an astronomer (born [[1734]]).
