{{Lunisolar May}} '''May 22''' is the 22nd day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|12=draft|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|12=draft|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenkei|ja|天慶|12=draft|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft}} [[938]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Shōhei|ja|承平 (日本)||12=draft}} to {{ill|Tenkei|ja|天慶|12=draft|12=draft}}. * [[Shōkyō]] 2nd year / [[Genkō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|12=draft}}) – The Kamakura shogunate was overthrown when [[Nitta Yoshisada]] attacked Kamakura, forcing about 800 members of the [[Hōjō]] clan, including {{ill|Hōjō Takatoshi|ja|北条高時|12=draft}}, to commit suicide.
== Births == * Genbun 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1737]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieharu|ja|徳川家治|12=draft}}, the 10th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[1786]]). * [[Bunka]] 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1815]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Asada Sōhaku|ja|浅田宗伯|12=draft}}, a physician of traditional Chinese medicine and Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=draft|12=draft}}) (died [[1894]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|12=draft|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|12=draft}} [[1859]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tsubouchi Shōyō|ja|坪内逍遙|12=draft}}, a novelist (died [[1935]]).
