{{afc comment|1=This article as with the other date articles is relatively limited in scope to Japan. Reviewing the translation of this is good and also adding content translated from Chinese and Korean wikipedias will also be good. Both wikipedias are also relatively centered around their own countries for their Lunisolar calendar dates[[User:Immanuelle|Immanuelle]] ([[User talk:Immanuelle|talk]]) 00:16, 28 April 2025 (UTC)}} {{Globalize|article|Japan|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Chinese|1=五月廿二|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Expand Korean|1=음력 5월 22일|topic=hist|date=April 2025}} {{Lunisolar May|qq=}} '''May 22''' is the 22nd day of the month {{ill|May (Lunisolar)|ja|5月 (旧暦)|lt=May (Satsuki)|qq=|12=draft}}, the 5th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|qq=|12=draft}}. Its {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|qq=|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Tomobiki|ja|友引|qq=|12=draft}}.
== Events == * {{ill|Tenkei|ja|天慶|qq=|12=draft}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[938]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Shōhei|ja|承平 (日本)||qq=|12=draft}} to {{ill|Tenkei|ja|天慶|qq=|12=draft}}. * [[Shōkyō]] 2nd year / [[Genkō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – The Kamakura shogunate was overthrown when [[Nitta Yoshisada]] attacked Kamakura, forcing about 800 members of the [[Hōjō]] clan, including {{ill|Hōjō Takatoshi|ja|北条高時|qq=|12=draft}}, to commit suicide.
== Births == * Genbun 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1737]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieharu|ja|徳川家治|qq=|12=draft}}, the 10th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died [[1786]]). * [[Bunka]] 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1815]] {{ill|June 29|ja|6月29日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Asada Sōhaku|ja|浅田宗伯|qq=|12=draft}}, a physician of traditional Chinese medicine and Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|qq=|12=draft}}) (died [[1894]]). * {{ill|Ansei|ja|安政|qq=|12=draft}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar|2=ja|3=グレゴリオ暦|4=fr|5=Calendrier grégorien|6=de|7=Gregorianischer Kalender|8=tl|9=Kalendaryong Gregoryano|10=ru|11=Григорианский календарь|ja|グレゴリオ暦|qq=|12=draft}} [[1859]] {{ill|June 22|ja|6月22日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Tsubouchi Shōyō|ja|坪内逍遙|qq=|12=draft}}, a novelist (died [[1935]]).
== Deaths == * [[Yōshō (Southern Song)|Yōshō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[422]] {{ill|June 27|ja|6月27日|qq=|12=draft}}) – Emperor Wu of the Southern Song (【劉裕】), the first Emperor of the Song dynasty (born [[356]]). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Motoki|ja|北条基時|qq=|12=draft}}, the 13th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1285]]). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Takatoshi|ja|北条高時|qq=|12=draft}}, the 14th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate and 9th Detsū (born [[1303]]). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|12=draft}} [[1333]] {{ill|July 4|ja|7月4日|qq=|12=draft}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Sadakazu|ja|北条貞顕|qq=|12=draft}}, the 15th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born [[1278]]). * [[Ryakuō]] 1st year / [[Engen