== Events == * {{ill|Tengyō|en|Tengyō|qid=Q1327340|lt=Tenkei|1=Tengyō}} 1st year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|938|en|938|qid=Q24794|lt=938|1=938}} {{ill|June 22|en|June 22|qid=Q2663|lt=June 22|1=June 22}}) – The era name was changed from {{ill|Jōhei|en|Jōhei|qid=Q1324874|lt=Shōhei|1=Jōhei}} to {{ill|Tengyō|en|Tengyō|qid=Q1327340|lt=Tenkei|1=Tengyō}}. * {{ill|Shōkyō|en|Shōkyō|qid=Q1069086|lt=Shōkyō|1=Shōkyō}} 2nd year / {{ill|Genkō|en|Genkō|qid=Q844859|lt=Genkō|1=Genkō}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}} {{ill|July 4|en|July 4|qid=Q2698|lt=July 4|1=July 4}}) – The Kamakura shogunate was overthrown when [[Nitta Yoshisada]] attacked Kamakura, forcing about 800 members of the {{ill|Later Hōjō clan|en|Later Hōjō clan|qid=Q431928|lt=Later Hōjō clan|1=Later Hōjō clan}} clan, including {{ill|Hōjō Takatoki|en|Hōjō Takatoki|qid=Q2355334|lt=Hōjō Takatoshi|1=Hōjō Takatoki}}, to commit suicide.
== Births == * Genbun 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1737|en|1737|qid=Q6993|lt=1737|1=1737}} {{ill|June 20|en|June 20|qid=Q2666|lt=June 20|1=June 20}}) – {{ill|Tokugawa Ieharu|en|Tokugawa Ieharu|qid=Q437518|lt=Tokugawa Ieharu|1=Tokugawa Ieharu}}, the 10th shōgun of the Tokugawa shogunate (died {{ill|1786|en|1786|qid=Q7760|lt=1786|1=1786}}). * {{ill|Bunka|en|Bunka|qid=Q1373146|lt=Bunka|1=Bunka}} 12nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1815|en|1815|qid=Q6948|lt=1815|1=1815}} {{ill|June 29|en|June 29|qid=Q2659|lt=June 29|1=June 29}}) – {{ill|Asada Sōhaku|ja|浅田宗伯|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Asada Sōhaku|1=Asada Sōhaku|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q6560684}}, a physician of traditional Chinese medicine and Confucian scholar ({{ill|Ru|ja|儒学者|zh|儒生|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ru|1=Ru (Confucian scholar)|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q125199930}}) (died {{ill|1894|en|1894|qid=Q7843|lt=1894|1=1894}}). * {{ill|Ansei|en|Ansei|qid=Q1327259|lt=Ansei|1=Ansei}} 6th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1859|en|1859|qid=Q7687|lt=1859|1=1859}} {{ill|June 22|en|June 22|qid=Q2663|lt=June 22|1=June 22}}) – {{ill|Tsubouchi Shōyō|ja|坪内逍遙|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tsubouchi Shōyō|ja_comment=jawiki redirects to 坪内逍遥|1=Tsubouchi Shōyō|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q706196}}, a novelist (died {{ill|1935|en|1935|qid=Q18658|lt=1935|1=1935}}).
== Deaths == * [[Yōshō (Southern Song)|Yōshō]] 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|422|en|422|qid=Q30906|lt=422|1=422}} {{ill|June 27|en|June 27|qid=Q2664|lt=June 27|1=June 27}}) – Emperor Wu of the Southern Song (【劉裕】), the first Emperor of the Song dynasty (born {{ill|356|en|356|qid=Q47937|lt=356|1=356}}). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}} {{ill|July 4|en|July 4|qid=Q2698|lt=July 4|1=July 4}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Mototoki|en|Hōjō Mototoki|qid=Q2490704|lt=Hōjō Motoki|1=Hōjō Mototoki}}, the 13th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born {{ill|1285|en|1285|qid=Q5546|lt=1285|1=1285}}). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}} {{ill|July 4|en|July 4|qid=Q2698|lt=July 4|1=July 4}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Takatoki|en|Hōjō Takatoki|qid=Q2355334|lt=Hōjō Takatoshi|1=Hōjō Takatoki}}, the 14th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate and 9th Detsū (born {{ill|1303|en|1303|qid=Q5614|lt=1303|1=1303}}). * Shōkyō 2nd year / Genkō 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1333|en|1333|qid=Q6004|lt=1333|1=1333}} {{ill|July 4|en|July 4|qid=Q2698|lt=July 4|1=July 4}}) – {{ill|Hōjō Sadaaki|en|Hōjō Sadaaki|qid=Q1083385|lt=Hōjō Sadakazu|1=Hōjō Sadaaki}}, the 15th Shikken of the Kamakura shogunate (born {{ill|1278|en|1278|qid=Q5533|lt=1278|1=1278}}). * {{ill|Ryakuō|en|Ryakuō|qid=Q1146182|lt=Ryakuō|1=Ryakuō}} 1st year / {{ill|Engen|en|Engen|qid=Q1194159|lt=Engen|1=Engen}} 3rd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|en|Julian calendar|qid=Q11184|lt=Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar}} {{ill|1338|en|1338|qid=Q6044|lt=1338|1=1338}} {{ill|June 10|en|June 10|qid=Q2615|lt=June 10|1=June 10}}) – {{ill|Kitabatake Akiie|en|Kitabatake Akiie|qid=Q1036864|lt=Kitabatake Akiie|1=Kitabatake Akiie}}, a military commander ({{ill|Busho (Rank)|ja|武将|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Busho (Rank)|1=military commander|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11545923}}) (born {{ill|1318|en|1318|qid=Q5755|lt=1318|1=1318}}). * {{ill|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|en|Tenshō (Momoyama period)|qid=Q1145058|lt=Tenshō Era|1=Tenshō (Momoyama period)}} 14th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1586|en|1586|qid=Q6739|lt=1586|1=1586}} {{ill|July 8|en|July 8|qid=Q2692|lt=July 8|1=July 8}}) – {{ill|Hachisuka Masakatsu|en|Hachisuka Masakatsu|qid=Q1201825|lt=Hachisuga Masakatsu|1=Hachisuka Masakatsu}}, a military commander (born {{ill|1526|en|1526|qid=Q6325|lt=1526|1=1526}}). * {{ill|Tenna|en|Tenna|qid=Q1145289|lt=Tenna|1=Tenna}} 2nd year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1682|en|1682|qid=Q7648|lt=1682|1=1682}} {{ill|June 27|en|June 27|qid=Q2664|lt=June 27|1=June 27}}) – {{ill|Ikeda Mitsumasa|en|Ikeda Mitsumasa|qid=Q3148401|lt=Ikeda Mitsumasa|1=Ikeda Mitsumasa}}, lord of the Okayama Domain in Bizen (born {{ill|1609|en|1609|qid=Q6762|lt=1609|1=1609}}). * {{ill|Hōei|en|Hōei|qid=Q1145262|lt=Hōei|1=Hōei}} 7th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1710|en|1710|qid=Q6861|lt=1710|1=1710}} {{ill|June 18|en|June 18|qid=Q2670|lt=June 18|1=June 18}}) – {{ill|Kawai Sōrō|ja|河合曾良|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Kawai Sōrō|1=Kawai Sora|comment=changed title based on wikidata|qid=Q11141924}}, a haiku poet and one of the disciples of Shōmon Jūtetsu (born {{ill|1649|en|1649|qid=Q6945|lt=1649|1=1649}}). * {{ill|Kansei|en|Kansei|qid=Q1195131|lt=Kansei|1=Kansei}} 11th year ({{ill|Gregorian calendar|en|Gregorian calendar|qid=Q12138|lt=Gregorian calendar|1=Gregorian calendar}} {{ill|1799|en|1799|qid=Q7827|lt=1799|1=1799}} {{ill|June 25|en|June 25|qid=Q2662|lt=June 25|1=June 25}}) – {{ill|Asada Goryu|en|Asada Goryu|qid=Q720222|lt=Asada Gōritsu|1=Asada Goryu}}, an astronomer (born {{ill|1734|en|1734|qid=Q6977|lt=1734|1=1734}}).
